### New Repository Checklist

1. Define aliases in `tsconfig.base.json` and configure project references in `tsconfig.json` (which references `tsconfig.app.json` and `tsconfig.node.json`).
2. Configure Tailwind tokens in `core/constants/designTokens.ts` and mirror in `tailwind.config.ts`.
3. Create initial domain `src/domains/<domain>` (use `scripts/generate.ts` if present).
4. Validate env in `core/config/env.client.ts`; add `public/runtime-config.json` if needed.
5. Enable providers in `app/providers` (Theme, Query, Auth, Analytics) as required.
6. Set up tests in `tests/setupTests.ts` with MSW and RTL; add first test.
7. Configure ESLint boundaries and Prettier (with Tailwind plugin).
8. Add lazy routes in `app/router.tsx` and `<domain>/routes.ts`.
9. Add error pages and mount a global error boundary.
10. Wire analytics/logging adapters only if needed for the project.
